# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
/build/
/coverage/

# pubspec.lock 不追踪——学生端/CI 自动 sync 会因 Flutter 版本不同导致 lock 降级漂移
# 开发者 clone 后请执行 flutter pub get 重新生成
/pubspec.lock

# Generated video intermediate assets
docs/video/**/audio/
docs/video/**/sent/
docs/video/**/slides/
docs/video/**/temp/
docs/video/**/crops/
docs/video/**/assets/

# ── 课件大文件 ──
# 视频/PPT 文件超出 Gitee 免费仓库 1GB 限制，不推送
# 应用通过 CoursewareDownloadService 从配置的资源地址获取
data/视频/
data/课件/秒出PPT/
data/课件/讯飞智文/
data/courseware_output/
video_output/
docs/video/generated/
docs/video/v3/
docs/video/v4/
docs/video/v5/
*.mp4
*.wav
*.avi
*.mov
*.pptx

# Windows reserved file accidentally created
nul

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release

# ── 敏感文件（签名/密钥/环境变量） ──
.env
.env.*
*.jks
